tool_description:
Real-time data, unofficial API realtor com, search for-sale and rental listings

Realtor is an online real estate marketplace that specializes in connecting buyers, sellers, and renters with properties across the United States. 

API allows users to search and explore a wide range of residential properties, including houses, condos, townhouses and apartments. 

Its extensive database of property listings, which is constantly updated to reflect the latest availability on the market. Users can ...

api_list.name: timezone
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://realtor-search.p.rapidapi.com/timezone"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "realtor-search.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
